arts.ttl: NAC Breda contact free agent Lamprou
arts.sum: NAC Breda have approached Kostas Lamprou to join during the winter break, Voetbal International have reported.

NAC Breda recently defeated Almere City 1-0 at home in their last Eredivisie match, ending a three-match winless streak. This victory put Almere City in seventh place with 19 points from 14 matches. ...
